Presenter mode

To enable presenter mode add ?presentme=true to the URL of the presentation. For example: my-presentation.html?presentme=true

The presenter mode window will open and will always re-open with the presentation until it is disabled with: my-presentation.html?presentme=false

Display Modes

  • ‘f’ enable fullscreen mode
  • ‘w’ toggle widescreen mode
  • ‘o’ enable overview mode
  • ‘h’ enable code highlight mode
  • ‘p’ show presenter notes
